ygData.messageBody:
I have a Halfling character and I've traveled through RunnyEye many
times going to the gorge to fight Minos or traveling to Qeynos. If I
remember right, I've seen Borxx on the first level in RunnyEye which
isn't so bad. I'm not certain, but I'll ask some friends as well.

From: Magik [mailto:aarongb@...]
Sent: Tuesday, April 20, 1999 12:59 PM
To: eqenchanters@onelist.com
Subject: [eqenchanters] (necessary spoiler, life and death)....forget
about this one till you WAAAAYY HIGHER!!!! (levels not drugs HAHA)


From: "Magik" <aarongb@...>

This quest is not for the faint of heart OR the faint
period....HAHAHAH!!!>...

Borxx is the actual leader of the Goblins of Runneye and can be
found in the bottom of the dungeon.....but heres the kiker....this
dungeon
is like levels 22 to 35 or 40.....HAHA!!>...so yeh could be fun but most
likely you wont make it passed the first couple doorways......sorry to
disappoint you but look forward to it for the future freind.....Im sure
it
will be a VERY worthy adventure!!!



Dymond....
